intended to help playing return of the mad god (rotmg) on kongregate
make sure, that the game and the surrounding black area are good visible
It searches the whole screen for this black color - so it might happen, that tabs with this specific color make the detection fail

What it does:
Inside constants the positions and colors are marked for healthbar and the money symbol of a healthpot
If health is below 50 percent it will press f

libraries used: PyMouse, gtk, and pykey
